"__you__to Germany before?"

249
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,700
Frase número 2:

250
00:12:07,780 --> 00:12:13,820
"She__ __ waiting for the doctor since 9am."

251
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,400
